snippet.textDisplay:
The reason why i started being a streamer on YouTube!

I was inspired by my love for video games & saw as i went on other platforms like Twitch/Youtube an saw other streamers having fun with it streaming the games they love. So i wanted to become one myself becuase i wanna take my passion for video games into another level into the content creation world. Sense i started at 13 Y/o from a Galaxy S3. Yeah i was that modivated. Streaming Minecraft PE at like 30 FPS. I really liked it & i loved it enough to become a part time streamer when i got enough money to buy some of the equipment for it. I still stream till this day halfway to 500 Subscribers at 20 years old & I wont ever give up fullfilling my dream to be a popular streamer as our mothers once taught us.


Dont ever give up on your dreams. Pursue them & im defiantly purseing mine!
